short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Supernero will enhance Dinero to be usefull for people not working in Dinero.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Supernero will help enhance and increase your workflow in Dinero Regnskab. It helps you do simple tasks as creating vouchers from transactions which eliminates the need for having multiple tabs open and switching between them. 

Supernero only works with Dinero Regnskab which is a Danish accounting system.
